\id COL - Ndendeule Bible Version 
\h Akakolochahe 
\toc1 Baluwa jha Pauli kwa Akakolochahe 
\toc2 Akakolochahe 
\toc3 Akak 
\mt2 Baluwa jha Pauli kwa 
\mt1 Akakolochahe 
\imt1 Ulongolelo 
\ip Baluwa jha Ntenga Pauli kwa Akakolochahe kikajhandikwe na Pauli mu chula jha 1:1. Akajhandike baluwa jhenje pakibha mukipungo pange pakibha ku muche gwa ku Loma muchaka cha makome chita pabhelwika njwe Yecho Kilichitu. Baluwa jhenje kwa Akakolochahe na baluwa jhela kwa Akaepecho na baluwa kwa Akafilemone ikemwa baluwa ya ku kipungo nhwalo Pauli akajhandike pakibha kwenio. Akajhandike baluwa kwa likunde lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu lilibhii ku muche gwa Kolochahe. Pauli akatumbulichejhe likunde lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu ku Kolochahe ngita chaichimulila mu chula jha 2:1, nambo apalitwa kulitangatila likunde lende lilinnyeketii Kilichitu. Pange iwechekana Epafula ndi jwatumbulicha lilongo lende lya bhando bhibhannyeketii Kilichitu nhwalo ahumila ku muche gwa ku Kolochahe. 
\ip Pauli akachitwichwe na mabholo ghuwange nkate jha lilongo lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu lya kwenio ku Kolochahe, chehemo jhenje ndi ikatoi pwache ngolonga kuchimulila nhwalo gwenio. Iwechekana pange pakibha na lilongo lya Akakilichitu lihembukilo lyabhe likibha kwa Akayahude bhubhajhighita kwachokolekeya Akakilichitu bhange bhankengame malaghilo ghabhe gha Kiyahude ghighaumila mu Lilaghano lya Makacho, na achwa kujhingii jando. Pauli akajhandike hotu kubhehe Akakilichitu bhipalwajhe kilebhe chochoha, nambo nga Kilichitu ndo, mu chula jha 1:15-20, na mabholo ghighahumita kwa bhando ghakwetejhe mana, mu chula jha 2:8. 
\iot Ghughabhii mukitabo 
\io1 Pauli atumbuu kulijhambucha lilongo lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu lya ku Kolochahe, mu chula jha 1:1-2. 
\io1 Peniya Pauli ijhandika ukolo gwa Kilichitu, na ndi pajhangwila kwa nhwalo gwa mabholo ghuwange ghighajhenii ku Kolochahe, mu chula jha 1:3-3:4. 
\io1 Ngita chayobalile mu baluwa yake yamahele, Pauli itumii nucho jhenge jha baluwa kwalaghalalikiya Akakilichitu chibhipalwa kutama, mu chula jha 3:5-4:6. 
\io1 Pauli ijhomolela kwa kwajhambucha kabhele na kwalaghalikii bhando kubhehe baluwa jhenje ichomwa palonge jhabhe kwa lilongo lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu na kwa bhando bhange, mu chula jha 4:7-18. 
\c 1  
\s1 Baluwa jha Pauli kwa Akakolochahe 
\p  
\v 1 Nenga Napauli, natenga jwa Yecho Kilichitu kwa kupala Chapanga, pamonga na Timocheyo nnongo gwito. 
\p  
\v 2 Punnyandikila mangota mabhando bha Chapanga bhumitama ku Kolochahe, makolongo bhito bhumuhobholeka kwa kulombana na Kilichitu. 
\p Tunnyopela umbone na uteeke kuhumii kwa Chapanga Tate gwito. 
\s1 Pauli inyopa Chapanga na kunchengula 
\p  
\v 3 Machiko ghoha putunnyopela tunchenguu Chapanga, Tate gwa Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu,  
\v 4 nhwalo tujhohine chimunhobholela Bhambo Yecho Kilichitu, na chimwapala bhando bhoha bha Chapanga.  
\v 5 Nhwalo gwa kihobholelo chino na upalo gwino lihobholelo lela limekwii kunane kwa Chapanga, ndi lela linyohina kuhumii makacho kwa lilobhe lya chakaka lya Lilobhe lya Mbone.  
\v 6 Lilobhe lya Mbone lyenio linhikilii mangota na kujhenela pannema ghoha na kuleta ghambone, ngita chiliteila kwino mangota kuhumii lichiko lela punyohina umbone gwa Chapanga na kumanya uteeke chiubhile.  
\v 7 Mukibholite umbone gwa Chapanga kuhumii kwa Epafula, nhenga lihengo nnyito jhutumpahii, ntumiche jwahobholeka jwa Kilichitu kunhwalo ghito.  
\v 8 Jwenio ndi jwatuchimulila malobhe gha upalo gwino ghupekiwe na Uhuke gwa Chapanga. 
\p  
\v 9 Kunhwalo gwenio kubhoke putujhohina malobhe ghino, tujhendelela kunyopela. Tunnyopa Chapanga ampelengane kumanya ghoha ghaghapala kwa malango ghoha na kumanya kutupatite na Uhuke gwa Chapanga.  
\v 10 Tujhopa yenio kupala nhoto kutama ngita chapala Bhambo, na nnyendelela kuhenga ghighanhalalicha jwenio. Na nnyendelela kuhenga ghughabhii ghambone na nchocha kukola mukumanya Chapanga.  
\v 11 Chapanga ampela makakala kwa uhotolo gwake mu ng'alicho nkolongwa nhoto kuhimbilila ghoha changatotokela.  
\v 12 Na kwa luheko muchengula Tate jwantehi mme chehemo jha mambu ghabhabhekii akanyahinyahi bhake mu unahota nkolongwa gwa lumule.  
\v 13 Jwenie ndi jwatughombwila kubhoke mu makakala gha lubhendo, na kutujhingiya munahota nkolongwa gwa Mwana mundo jwampala,  
\v 14 kupete kwa jwenio tughombokoka na kulekekewa uhakaho gwito. 
\s1 Kilichitu na lihengo lyake 
\q1  
\v 15 Kilichitu jhumumwene alandine njwe na Chapanga jwangabhonekana. Jwenio akibha kabula jha ihumbi yoha kupanganwa. 
\q1  
\v 16 Nhwalo kupete jwenie, Chapanga akapangine ilebhe yoha, 
\q1 ibhii kunane kwa Chapanga na ibhii pannema, 
\q1 ibhonekana na yangabhoneka, ibhehe ihumbi ya kihuke ibhii na makakala na, 
\q1 akanahota na bhibhalongocha na bhubhabhii na ukindendeke. 
\q1 Yoha ikapanginwe kupete jwenio na kwa nhwalo gwake. 
\q1  
\v 17 Kilichitu akibha kabula jha ilebhe yoha, ilebhe yoha ikamulana nde pamonga kwa jwenio. 
\q1  
\v 18 Jwenio ndi muto gwa yegha, yegha jhene ndi lilongo lya bhando bhibhanyeketii jwenio. Kilichitu ndi lihembuko lya ughome gwa yegha jhene. Jwenio ndi jwayokichwa abhehe jwakutumbula kwa ilebhe yoha. 
\q1  
\v 19 Nhwalo Chapanga jwenio akahalalichwe ukamilicho gwake ghoha ubhehe nkate jha Kilichitu. 
\q1  
\v 20 Kupete Mwana mundo, ilebhe yoha ijhelanichwe na Chapanga jwenio, na kwa miyahe jhake jhijhitike pa nchalaba aleta uteeke na ilebhe yoha ibhii pannema na ibhii kunane kwa Chapanga. 
\p  
\v 21 Peniya makacho mangota mukibha kutale na Chapanga na helahela mukibha akamakoko bhake nhwalo gwa malango ghino ghanganandela na matendwa ghino ghanganandela.  
\v 22 Nambo ngohe, Chapanga antei mangota akakoche mundo kupetele kuwe kwa yegha jha Mwana mundo, ndi ampeleke palonge jhake kongo mmii nyahinyahi na bhamaha changalemwa.  
\v 23 Nambo chimupalwa, nnyendelela kukikamulii kihobholelo chino kone nchengwitwe mu chinge nganganga, hilu nkotoka kujheketela kunyuanyua kubhoke mu lihobholelo lela lipilwe pala punyohina Lilobhe lya Mbone. Ne Pauli ndeilwe natumiche jwa Lilobhe lya Mbone ndi lilitangichwe kwa bhando bhoha bha pannema. 
\s1 Lihengo lya Pauli kwa lilongo lya bhando lilinnyeketii Kilichitu 
\p  
\v 24 Ngohe nihanganila kung'ahika kwa nhwalo gwino mangota, mitweleya jhegha jhango kwa ghala ghighapongwii mumang'ahiko gha Kilichitu kwa nhwalo jha yegha jhake ndi lilongo lya bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu.  
\v 25 Na nenga mekwite na Chapanga mme natumiche jwa lilongo lya bhando bhubhanyeketii Kilichitu. Ambii lihengo lya kutangacha Lilobhe lya umbone gwake gwamaha,  
\v 26 lijhambu lyenio ndi chile jhela jhikahihitwe kuhumii kwa bhando machiko ghoha ghangapeta, nambo ngohe iyekulilwe kwa bhando bhake.  
\v 27 Chapanga akapahile kwatenda bhando bhake bhamanye ulohe na ukolongwa gwa chile jhenje nkate jha nnema ghoha, na jhene ndi jhenje, Kilichitu abhii nkate jhino na nhwalo gwenio ulangiya mangota natujhingila mung'alicho gwa Chapanga ghuuhobholeka.  
\v 28 Ndi mana tutangacha Kilichitu kwa bhando bhoha na kwa malango ghoha, tunkelebhuwa na kubhola mundo jhojhoha kupala tuhoto kunneta kila mundo palonge jha Chapanga kone abhii akomile mu kolombana na Kilichitu.  
\v 29 Kutangacha lilobhe lyenio, nenga ndenda kughagha kone nitumii likakala lya Kilichitu lilihenga lihengo nkate jhango. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Mbala umanyengane chinighagha kuhenga lihengo kwa nhwalo gwino mangota, kwa mabhando bha ku kilambo chu ku Laodikiya na bhando bhala bhangakongana na nenga.  
\v 2 Ndenda yenio nipala kwaleke mwojho na bhakilombe mulipalano kupala bhamanye kwa chakaka, nabhamanye njwe chile jha Chapanga, bhihoto kuimanya chile jhene ndi Kilichitu jwenio.  
\v 3 Nkate jhake ihihitwe ihukilo yoha ya malango nu kumanya. 
\p  
\v 4 Ninobholela mangannyekete jhe mundo jhojhoha ankolowe kwa malobhe ghuwange ata ghahalalila bhole.  
\v 5 Pamonga nenga kubhehe kutale na mangota, nambo mwojho ubhii peniya pamonga na mangota, na nihangana punimmona chimuhenga mahengo ghino kwa ndela jha mbone chimuhobholela Kilichitu kwa uchakaka. 
\s1 Ughome gwa chakaka ubhii kwa kulombana na Kilichitu 
\p  
\v 6 Ngohe ngita chimunnyeketila Yecho Kilichitu kubhehe Bhambo, ndi nnyendelela hele kulombana nako.  
\v 7 Mme na ngegha nkate jhake, na ughome gwino uchengwike panane jhake na mukikamwii kihobholelo ngita chimolitwe, na mangota nchengule. 
\p  
\v 8 Mukilolekeye na mundo jhojhoha akotoka kunkolowa mangota kwa mabholo ghake gha jhajhe na ghuwange chika, ghighahobholela mapokelo gha bhando na michuka jhilongocha nnema, nambo ghahumajhe kwa Kilichitu jwenio!  
\v 9 Nhwalo nkate jha Kilichitu, muyegha jhake utama ukamilicho ghoha gwa Chapanga,  
\v 10 na mangota nkwete ughome telatela mu kulombana na jwenio. Jwenio abhii panane jha makakala ghoha gha kihuke na ukindendeke. 
\p  
\v 11 Kwa kulombana na Kilichitu mangota nnyingi jando kuhengwa jhe na bhando na kuileka yegha jha makacho jha uhakaho, nambo chi ngita chibhahenga bhando. Kukutendwa na Kilichitu jwenio kwa kukombolwa kuhumii muyegha jha uhakaho.  
\v 12 Nhwalo pubatichwa, mukachikitwe pamonga na Kilichitu, na muubaticho mangota helahela mukayokichwe pamonga na jwenio kuhumii mubaticho pala pumaghahobholila makakala gha Chapanga, ndi jwayokicha Yecho kuhumii muweghe  
\v 13 Mangota mwe helahela makacho mukibha ngita nhwelingine kwa nhwalo gwa uhakaho gwino na nhwalo gwa umundo gwino gwanganandela ghubhii na uhakaho. Nambo ngohe Chapanga antei mangota mme maghome pamonga na Kilichitu. Chapanga atulekekiye uhakaho gwito ghoha,  
\v 14 pajhomolila kuputa matakalilo ghito ghighajhandikwe na malaghilo gha kutuhadabuu twenga, ngakangila kutale, na ngakong'ondila pa nchalaba.  
\v 15 Panchalaba gwenio Kilichitu ndi pabhapokita makakala ghabhe bheniya ilongoche ya michuka na akanahota, ajhakwaleke hone palonge jha bhando kwatalaha ngita bhando bhibhapukilwe kungondo kwa langii kubhehe abhalepelii jhe. 
\p  
\v 16 Ngohe mangalogwa jhe mundo amekila nhwilo muchakulya amu muinywegho amu munyagho amu unyagho gwa kuhembukii mwehe amu mu Lichiko lya Kupomolela.  
\v 17 Ilebhe yenio ndi kiyeka tu cha ilebhe ipala kuhika, nambo uchakaka gwenie ubhii nkate jha Kilichitu.  
\v 18 Mangajhekete jhe kuhadabulwa na mundo jhojhoha jwakitenda jwamaha kwa nhwalo gwa uloto gwake na ndi aghaghalila unyenyekeho kwangachakaka kwa kwajhinamii akatumiche bha kunane kwa Chapanga, mundo ngita jwenio akiloka kwa nhwalo gwa ilebhe yaihwene na kwa nhwalo gwa malango ghake,  
\v 19 akilekite kukikamulii pamonga na Kilichitu, ndi jwabhii muto gwa yegha. Kupetele Kilichitu yegha jhoha ukamulana na kulombana pamonga kwa ihungo na micheketa jhake, na ukola ngita chapala Chapanga. 
\s1 Kuwegha na kutama pamonga na Kilichitu 
\p  
\v 20 Mangota nhwile pamonga na Kilichitu na nkombolilwe kuhumii mu makakala gha ilongoche bhibhalongocha nnema. Nhwalo gwa nike ngohe mitama ngita bhando bha nnema ghongone? Kabhele nhwalo gwa nike mukamuu malaghilo ngita ghenagha,  
\v 21 “Mangakamu jhe chenje amu nkotoka kupaha chenje amu nkotoka kupapaya chela!”  
\v 22 Ilebhe yenio yoha ukomelekeya pitumika, gheniya malaghilo na mabholo gha bhando tu.  
\v 23 Chakaka malaghilo gheniya ghibhonekana ghina malango mu kunyinamila ghabhatungite bhene, na unyenyekeho kwangabhehe na uchakaka mukuilongocha yegha kwa ukale, nambo ghakwetejhe makakala gha kuhibhilikiya tama jha yegha. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Ngohe anda uyokichwe pamonga na Kilichitu, uwachila mambu gha kunane kwa Chapanga, kwabhii Kilichitu, kwenio itama chehemo jha ulongoche jha lubhoko lwalelo lwa Chapanga.  
\v 2 Uwachila mambu gha kunane kwa Chapanga, yenio chi mambu gha pannema pano.  
\v 3 Nhwalo mangota uwilingine, na ughome gwino uhiitwe pamonga na Kilichitu nkate jha Chapanga.  
\v 4 Ughome gwino gwa chakaka ndi Kilichitu, na papala kupitila kabhele na mangota nampitila pamonga na jwenie mung'alicho! 
\s1 Ughome gwa makacho na ughome nhyono 
\p  
\v 5 Bhahe, nkome kila kilebhe changanandela chikibhii nkate jhino, ngongola na kuhenga ghanganandela na tama ya kubhehe na ilebhe ndii na mawacho ghanganandela na kijhaka chikilandana na kuijhinamii inyagho.  
\v 6 Kwa nhwalo gwa gheniya ghoha Chapanga nabhabhekela lilaka bhando bhoha bhangampala kunnyokanikiya.  
\v 7 Makacho mangota ntamita hele, punongwichwa na gheniya ghanganandela. 
\p  
\v 8 Nambo ngoheno mughaleke gheniya ghoha, lilaka na njoghololo na maligho na manganigha jhe Chapanga na mangalonge jhe malobhe ghanganandela pannomo gwino.  
\v 9 Mangakoloyana jhe, nhwalo mangota mulekite umundo gwa makacho pamonga na matendwa ghake ghoha ghanganandela,  
\v 10 na muhwalite umundo nhyono. Ghutendwa nhyono mumanye Chapanga kwa uchakaka, na kulandana na jwenio jwapangana umundo nhyono.  
\v 11 Peniya palekine jhe pakate jha mundo jwa kilambo chenge na Uyahude, jwajhingii jando na jwangajhingii jando, akaghene amu jwangachoma na mmanda amu jwangabhehe mmanda. Nambo Kilichitu ndi ghoha, na jwenio abhii mughoha. 
\p  
\v 12 Kwa nhwalo mangota ndi bhando bha Chapanga, jwenio akampahile na ahagwile mme bhando bhake, ngohe nkola kiya na umbone na unyenyekeho na utokomalo na luhimba.  
\v 13 Nhimbililane na kulekekehana anda mundo pakate jhino ankokolekeya nnyake. Mupalwa kulekekehana malemo ngita Bhambo chanenekekeya mangota.  
\v 14 Kuchocha kwa gheniya, nnyonjekeye kupalana, nhwalo upalo ulombikana ghoha nde kwa uchakaka.  
\v 15 Na uteeke gwa Kilichitu ulongoche umwojho gwino, nhwalo Chapanga ankemite mangota mme yegha jhimo. Kabhele mma na luchengulo!  
\v 16 Lilobhe lya Kilichitu litwelela twe mwenio nkate jhino. Mmolane na kukelebhuhana kwa malango ghoha. Kone nnyemba Zabule na mihambo jha kunnomba Chapanga na nnyembengane mihambo jha kunchenguu Chapanga kumiojho jhino.  
\v 17 Kila chimuhenga amu kukilongela, ntendengane yoha kwa liina lya Bhambo gwito Yecho Kilichitu kone muchengula Chapanga Tate kupete jwenio. 
\s1 Mabholo kwa nyumba 
\p  
\v 18 Na mangota akakeghe, majhokanikiya akangana bhino, yenio ndi chapala Bhambo. 
\p  
\v 19 Na mangota akanalome, mapale akahana bhino na nkotoka kwalakalila bheniya. 
\p  
\v 20 Na mangota akayana mwajhokanikiya akatate bhino machiko ghoha, yenio ndi chinhalalila Bhambo. 
\p  
\v 21 Na mangota akatate, nkotoka kwachimwa yana hino, anda nahajhe nabhahengeleka mwojho. 
\p  
\v 22 Na mangota akabhanda majhokanikiya akanahota bhino mughoha. Chi pibhannolokeya tugha kupala mmonekane bhambone, nambo ntenda gheniya kwa mwojho gwambone nhwalo gwa kunnyeketela Bhambo Yecho.  
\v 23 Chochoha chimuhenga, nhenge kwa mwojho ghoha, anda muntende Bhambo Yecho na chi nhwalo gwa mundo.  
\v 24 Nkomboka kubhehe Bhambo nampelengana ndweko yabhekite kwa bhando bhake. Chakaka Kilichitu ndi Bhambo jhumutumikila!  
\v 25 Nhwalo kila mundo jwatenda ghanganandela, napokela malepo ghanganandela ghake, nhwalo Chapanga abaghuu jhe bhando. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Na mangota akanahota, mwatendelengana akabhanda bhino ghambone na ngita chapala Chapanga, kone nkombokela na mangota helahela nkwete Bhambo kunane kwa Chapanga. 
\s1 Malaghilo 
\p  
\v 2 Munnyope Chapanga changatotokela, na pumunyopa Chapanga mukilolekeya na kunchenguu Chapanga.  
\v 3 Helahela mutujhopela na twenga kupala Chapanga atujhoghojolele nnyango gwa kutangacha Lilobhe tutangache chile jha Kilichitu. Kwa nhwalo gwa Lilobhe lya Mbone nenga ngohe mmi mu kipungo.  
\v 4 Ngohe unyopele nhoto kulongele ngita chiipala chile kulongelwa meke mbegha chile jhene. 
\p  
\v 5 Mme na malango palonge jha bhando bhangannyeketele Kilichitu, nkachane kutumii mbone kila pwache jhiminajho.  
\v 6 Machiko ghoha nnongela ghaumbone na gha kwajhangatii bhando, na umanye kwajhanguu mbone bhando machiko ghoha. 
\s1 Nyambucho jha kujhomolela 
\p  
\v 7 Tikiko nnongo gwito jhutumpahile, na ntumiche jwahobholeka na ntumiche nnyito mulihengo lya Bhambo, nanobholela mihalo jhango jhoha.  
\v 8 Ndi nhwalo nintuma kwino ankangamalicha mwojho gwino kwa kunnobholela malobhe ghito.  
\v 9 Ahika kwenio pamonga na Onechimo, nnongo gwito jhutumpala na jwahobholeka jweniojho ndi nnyino. Jwenio ndi nnyino nanongolela mihalo jha ilebhe itendika pambano. 
\p  
\v 10 Alisitako, jwatabhitwe pamonga na nenga, inyambucha pamonga na Maluku nnongo mundo Banaba helahela inyambucha. Mukajhohine njwe malaghilo ghake. Papala kuhika kwino mupokele.  
\v 11 Na jwenio Yochuwa helahela jwakemitwa Yusito, jhunyohina mihalo jhake inyambucha. Pakate jha Akayahude bhibhapokii kihobholelo njwe, bhamba tu kanjika bhibhahenga lihengo pamonga na nenga kwa nhwalo gwa Unahota nkolongwa gwa Chapanga, bhene ndi bhingangamalicha hake nenga. 
\p  
\v 12 Epafula, mundo jwa kilambo chino, ntumiche jwa Yecho Kilichitu inyambucha. Machiko ghoha jwenio ighagha kunyopela kwa Chapanga nnyemangane nganganga, nkomale na nnyendelela kuhobholela na kuhenga ghighanhalalicha Chapanga.  
\v 13 Nihoto kulonge ahenga lihengo kwa nhwalo gwino mangota na kwa nhwalo gwa bhando bha ku Laodikiya na bhala bhubhabhii ku Hilapole.  
\v 14 Luka, jhola nng'anga gwito jhutumpala na Dema bhinyambucha. 
\p  
\v 15 Mwajhambuche akalongo bhito bhubhabhii ku Laodikiya na nnombo gwito Nifa pamonga na lilongo lyoha lya bhando lilinyeketii Kilichitu lilikongana kajhake.  
\v 16 Anda nnyomolela kuchoma baluwa jhenje, mwapela bhajhino bhibhanyeketii Kilichitu bhu ku Laodikeya na bhene bhaichome, na baluwa jhinajhandikile bhando bhu ku Laodikiya na mangota bhampele nchome.  
\v 17 Na munobholele Alukipo, “Nyomole lihengo lyapokii kuhumii kwa Bhambo.” 
\p  
\v 18 Ne Pauli nyandike ghanga kwa lubhoko lwango namwete, ninyambucha. Nkomboka nenga mmii mukipungo! 
\p Naninyopela umbone kubhoke kwa Chapanga.